\s1 The Response of God  
\p
\v 16  \w The|strong="H3588"\w* \nd \+w Lord|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* said \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w Moses|strong="H4872"\w*, “Gather \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w me|strong="H3947"\w* \w seventy|strong="H7657"\w* \w men|strong="H2205"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w elders|strong="H2205"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w Israel|strong="H3478"\w*, \w whom|strong="H1992"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w know|strong="H3045"\w* \w are|strong="H1992"\w* \w elders|strong="H2205"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w people|strong="H5971"\w* \w and|strong="H4872"\w* \w officials|strong="H7860"\w* \w over|strong="H3068"\w* \w them|strong="H1992"\w*, \w and|strong="H4872"\w* \w bring|strong="H3947"\w* \w them|strong="H1992"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* tent \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w meeting|strong="H4150"\w*; let \w them|strong="H1992"\w* \w take|strong="H3947"\w* \w their|strong="H3068"\w* position \w there|strong="H8033"\w* \w with|strong="H5973"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w*.  
