\s1 The Response of the Lord  
\p
\v 4  \w The|strong="H3068"\w* \nd \+w Lord|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* spoke \w immediately|strong="H6597"\w* \w to|strong="H3318"\w* \w Moses|strong="H4872"\w*, Aaron, \w and|strong="H4872"\w* \w Miriam|strong="H4813"\w*: “\w The|strong="H3068"\w* \w three|strong="H7969"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w you|strong="H3318"\w* \w come|strong="H3318"\w* \w to|strong="H3318"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* tent \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w meeting|strong="H4150"\w*.” \w So|strong="H3318"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w three|strong="H7969"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w them|strong="H3318"\w* \w went|strong="H3318"\w*.  
