\v 40  So Moses told the Israelites everything, just as the \nd Lord\nd* had commanded him.   
\c 30  
\p
\v 1  \w Moses|strong="H4872"\w* \w told|strong="H6680"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* leaders \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* tribes \w concerning|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w Israelites|strong="H3478"\w*, “\w This|strong="H3068"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* what \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \nd \+w Lord|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* \w has|strong="H3068"\w* \w commanded|strong="H6680"\w*:  
\v 2  \w If|strong="H1121"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w man|strong="H1121"\w* \w makes|strong="H1696"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* vow \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \nd \+w Lord|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* \w or|strong="H1121"\w* takes \w an|strong="H3068"\w* \w oath|strong="H1697"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* binding obligation \w on|strong="H3068"\w* \w himself|strong="H3068"\w*, \w he|strong="H3068"\w* \w must|strong="H1121"\w* \w not|strong="H2088"\w* \w break|strong="H3068"\w* \w his|strong="H3068"\w* \w word|strong="H1697"\w*, \w but|strong="H1696"\w* \w must|strong="H1121"\w* \w do|strong="H3068"\w* whatever \w he|strong="H3068"\w* \w has|strong="H3068"\w* \w promised|strong="H1696"\w*.   
\s1 Vows Made by Single Women  
\p
\v 3 “\w If|strong="H3588"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* young woman \w who|strong="H3605"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w still|strong="H3588"\w* \w living|strong="H5315"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w her|strong="H3605"\w* father’s house \w makes|strong="H6213"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w vow|strong="H5088"\w* \w to|strong="H3318"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \nd \+w Lord|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* \w or|strong="H3808"\w* \w places|strong="H3605"\w* \w herself|strong="H5315"\w* \w under|strong="H5921"\w* \w an|strong="H6213"\w* obligation,  
\v 4  \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w her|strong="H3588"\w* father hears \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w her|strong="H3588"\w* \w vow|strong="H5088"\w* \w or|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* obligation \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w which|strong="H3068"\w* \w she|strong="H3588"\w* \w has|strong="H3068"\w* pledged herself, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w her|strong="H3588"\w* father remains silent \w about|strong="H1004"\w* \w her|strong="H3588"\w*, \w then|strong="H3588"\w* \w all|strong="H3068"\w* \w her|strong="H3588"\w* \w vows|strong="H5088"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* stand, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w every|strong="H3068"\w* obligation \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w which|strong="H3068"\w* \w she|strong="H3588"\w* \w has|strong="H3068"\w* pledged herself \w will|strong="H3068"\w* stand.  
\v 5  \w But|strong="H8085"\w* if \w her|strong="H3605"\w* father overrules \w her|strong="H3605"\w* \w when|strong="H8085"\w* \w he|strong="H3605"\w* \w hears|strong="H8085"\w* \w about|strong="H5921"\w* \w it|strong="H5921"\w*, \w then|strong="H6965"\w* \w none|strong="H3605"\w* \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \w her|strong="H3605"\w* \w vows|strong="H5088"\w* \w or|strong="H8085"\w* \w her|strong="H3605"\w* obligations \w which|strong="H8085"\w* \w she|strong="H5921"\w* \w has|strong="H5315"\w* pledged \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w herself|strong="H5315"\w* \w will|strong="H5315"\w* \w stand|strong="H6965"\w*. \w And|strong="H6965"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \nd Lord\nd* \w will|strong="H5315"\w* release \w her|strong="H3605"\w* \w from|strong="H5921"\w* \w it|strong="H5921"\w*, \w because|strong="H5921"\w* \w her|strong="H3605"\w* father overruled \w her|strong="H3605"\w*.   
\s1 Vows Made by Married Women  
\p
\v 6 “\w And|strong="H6965"\w* \w if|strong="H3588"\w* \w she|strong="H3588"\w* marries \w a|strong="H3068"\w* husband \w while|strong="H3117"\w* \w under|strong="H5921"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w vow|strong="H5088"\w*, \w or|strong="H3808"\w* \w she|strong="H3588"\w* uttered \w anything|strong="H3605"\w* impulsively \w by|strong="H5921"\w* \w which|strong="H3068"\w* \w she|strong="H3588"\w* \w has|strong="H3068"\w* pledged \w herself|strong="H5315"\w*,  
