\s1 Vows Made by Widows  
\p
\v 9 “\w But|strong="H8085"\w* \w every|strong="H3117"\w* \w vow|strong="H5088"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* widow \w or|strong="H8085"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* divorced woman \w which|strong="H3068"\w* \w she|strong="H5921"\w* \w has|strong="H3068"\w* pledged \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w herself|strong="H5315"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* remain \w intact|strong="H5921"\w*.  
